arty, PDP, Sunday, described the victory of the candidate of the party, Senator Ademola Adeleke in the Saturday's gubernatorial election as the affirmation of Osun people's will In "Osun election" TMG, Monday, commended performance and improvement by the Independent National Electoral Commission, INEC, in conducting the just concluded Osun governorship election. In "News"